   "id": "video_moment:timed-flux-cored-setup-from-scratch",
   "type": "video_moment",
   "name": "Timed flux-cored setup from scratch",
   "summary": "Starting with a new spool not installed and all leads disconnected, the presenter times himself setting up the OmniPro 220 for flux-cored welding, taking 4.5 minutes total including wire loading and lead connections.",
