   "id": "video_moment:flux-cored-test-welds-on-plate-and-coupons",
   "type": "video_moment",
   "name": "Flux-cored test welds on plate and coupons",
   "summary": "A flat horizontal weld on 3/16 inch plate and a fillet weld on 1/8 inch coupons are performed using .035 Vulcan flux-cored wire with the synergic auto settings, both turning out well.",
